## VISUAL DESIGN FOR ARTICLE LINKS

### Button Style 1: "Read Full System" (Primary)
- Color: Teal (primary brand color)
- Text: "[READ FULL SYSTEM & GET TEMPLATES] →"
- Placement: At end of system teaser
- Action: Opens full article in new tab

### Button Style 2: "Learn More" (Secondary)
- Color: Light teal outline
- Text: "See the full breakdown →"
- Placement: In problem statements
- Action: Links to relevant article

### Button Style 3: "Article Hub" (Footer)
- Color: Orange (secondary brand color)
- Text: "Explore all articles"
- Placement: Footer, FAQ, final CTA
- Action: Links to blog hub with all 6 articles

