## SEO BENEFITS OF THIS STRUCTURE

### Benefit 1: Internal Linking
- Homepage links to 6+ internal blog articles
- Distributes page authority throughout site
- Google sees you as comprehensive resource
- Improves rankings for all pages

### Benefit 2: Long-Form Content
- 6 articles × 2,000-5,000 words each = 12,000-30,000 words of content
- Google loves deep, authoritative content
- Ranks for hundreds of long-tail keywords
- Contractors find you through problem-specific searches

### Benefit 3: Multiple Entry Points
- Contractor searches "HVAC quote follow-up" → finds Article 1
- Contractor searches "marketing ROI" → finds Article 5
- Contractor searches "after-hours emergency calls" → finds Article 3
- Each article drives traffic to homepage

### Benefit 4: Trust & Authority Signals
- Depth of content signals expertise
- Free resources signal confidence
- Detailed ROI math signals credibility
- Comprehensive framework signals mastery

